 Why Do Humans Get Emotionally Attached?
From infant to adult, people are almost linked through
attachment. Attachment often creates a trigger bomb in 
your brain. Emotional attachment starts connecting to you
even indirectly.

It is only in love for your partner that people say it is
for deeply whom you care. You become emotionally dependent
on that one person. Your brain loves that person when they
are not around and starts craving for more.

Emotions are basic needs of a system where new and creative
ideas develop through a pattern called obsession.

## Why Do People Seek Validation From Others?
The only loss is when someone's opinion matters more to you
than your own thoughts.

How you were raised as a kid is how you seek love as an adult.
If parents were not giving attention, you start seeking 
attention from outside.

Constantly praising for attention from outside gave you 
temporary peace, while you were left with nothing but 
approval of others. Think about yourself first.
